In payload, set:
assignUser = your UI ID (example: SG0923042)
Ensure your user ID has email in mapping:
sql

IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM CA_USER_EMAILS_T WHERE UI_USER_ID = 'SG0923042')
BEGIN
  INSERT INTO CA_USER_EMAILS_T (UI_USER_ID, SEQ_NUM, EMAIL_ADDRESS)
  VALUES ('SG0923042', 1, 'sourabh.gupta@optum.com');
END
ELSE
BEGIN
  UPDATE CA_USER_EMAILS_T
  SET EMAIL_ADDRESS = 'sourabh.gupta@optum.com'
  WHERE UI_USER_ID = 'SG0923042';
END





